{"tid":2348961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨發布片段：披露12港人案中的證物 並宣稱會扣減羈押期「很快便可回家」","createTime":"2021-01-01T07:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T08:04:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa24614a244c0689a7d1b82ea3fcb42fc16bcc6","tid":2348961,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"【12港人】官媒公開涉案證物 稱涉案人權利獲「依法保障」<br />\n<br />\n12港人案周三（30日）於深圳鹽田法院宣判，10人被判囚7個月至3年不等，2名未成年者不獲起訴移交香港扣押。有內地官媒昨（31日）公開聲稱涉案證物片段，亦披露審訊更多細節。<br />\n<br />\n官媒深圳廣電集團深圳衛視旗下《直新聞》發布片段，稱首次披露案中查獲證物，包括船隻、釣魚竿等。<br />\n<br />\n案中被控組織他人偷越邊境罪的鄧棨然及喬映瑜，分別判監3年及2年。片段指法院審明，船隻上檢獲的衛星電話及涉案人Telegram群組內資訊顯示，鄧棨然、喬映瑜在「上家」的指揮下，聯絡、溝通其餘涉案人員，策劃、組織由香港偷渡至台灣。片段又指鄧棨然負責購買涉事船隻，並在「上家」的安排下學習船隻基本駕駛技能。片段指法院認為兩名被告組織偷渡人數眾多，已構成組織他人偷越邊境罪。<br />\n<br />\n另一片段稱，涉案港人在判決前已被拘留，因此羈押一日抵扣刑期一日，「意味著刑期也將大幅縮短，很快他們便可回家」。<br />\n<br />\n該片段亦稱，在之前的刑事拘留，案件偵查及審查起訴等階段，涉案人「依法享有各項權利」。片段稱深圳檢察機關依法為辯護律師閱卷提供各種履職便利，充分保障涉案人員的訴訟權利。<br />\n<br />\n然而多名涉案家屬指出，當局拒絕承認家屬委托的律師，亦有律師疑受壓退出。至於聲稱為子女自願委托的「官派律師」資料不詳，有家屬現在仍未能取得聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n另一片段重申，基於屬地管轄原則，內地司法系統對案件享有無可爭議的管轄權，可以質疑行使細節，惟不能質疑管轄權本身。<br />\n<br />\n《直新聞》片段截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wg65EnZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwg65EnZ.jpg&h=23617c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CupidProducer/photos/a.132326504098068/717547352242644/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCupidProducer%2Fphotos%2Fa.132326504098068%2F717547352242644%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=ca4a5d23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CupidProducer/photos/a.132326504098068/717547352242644/</a>"},{"pid":"646ab40deb964bf45b2a1bba22629e6e9d093688","tid":2348961,"uid":355064,"like":5,"dislike":28,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔今次輸到一鋪清袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8071dada9081984966b01fa0561028dbcb50d3fb","tid":2348961,"uid":18477,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"<del><span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"pink\">依法</span></span></del><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">綁架</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ab56a04dc1309516a506851db2782601b36f8158","tid":2348961,"uid":219475,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"646ab40deb964bf45b2a1bba22629e6e9d093688","tid":2348961,"uid":355064,"like":5,"dislike":28,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔今次輸到一鋪清袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"輸乜鳩?解釋黎聽下"},{"pid":"9dbf20f7a44974241eb6cd47fafc19a8379a4b4b","tid":2348961,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"扣左四個月仲有三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855f52ff7c36145b738192115c4f15ede1930110","tid":2348961,"uid":18477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔今次輸到一鋪清袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又冇電又冇得燒柴過唔過到冬呀已封鎖會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f640e5ec10e1bb57d92ef93571f347f41e6cf780","tid":2348961,"uid":58958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ab56a04dc1309516a506851db2782601b36f8158","tid":2348961,"uid":219475,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"646ab40deb964bf45b2a1bba22629e6e9d093688","tid":2348961,"uid":355064,"like":